#. Add-on summary/title, usually the user visible name of the add-on
#. Translators: Summary/title for this add-on
#. to be shown on installation and add-on information found in add-on store
#: buildVars.py:21
msgid "Contacts Manager for NVDA"
msgstr "Gerenciador de contatos para NVDA"

#. Add-on description
#. Translators: Long description to be shown for this add-on on add-on information from add-on store
#: buildVars.py:24
msgid ""
"Simple contacts manager for saving phone numbers, emails, and other contact "
"details for personal or professional use.\n"
"\n"
"Shortcut Windows+Alt+L."
msgstr ""
"Gerenciador de contatos simples para salvar números de telefone, e-mails e "
"outros detalhes de contato para uso pessoal ou profissional.\n"
"\n"
"Atalho Windows+Alt+L."

